description: Perched above the city, this stunning South Boston penthouse delivers jaw-dropping panoramic views from your private roof deck—the perfect spot for morning coffee or sunset cocktails. Need more outdoor space? You’ve got it with a direct-access back deck, offering even more room to relax or grill out with guests. The living room sets the scene for cozy nights, while central AC keeps things comfortable year-round. This unit offers two large bedrooms with great closets and a bonus room perfect for a home office or nursery. This PET-FRIENDLY building has low fees and NO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS, offering incredible potential as a primary residence or a fantastic investment opportunity. Additional conveniences include private laundry and storage in the basement, ensuring you have all the space you need. Located just moments from Southie’s hottest spots on Broadway, the beach, and with easy access to both the Seaport and Downtown, this condo is truly city living at its absolute best!
